blueprint.label: Bulk Launch System
blueprint.description:
Launch bulk material by cargo rocket.  Set silo destination by name and "launch on cargo full".

This can support up to 5 rockets by duplicating the rocket silo and surrounding logic alongside the station and changing the number of capsules in the combinator to match the number of silos (prevents idle capsules on the belt).  Connect power & red wire along the top.

Add item requests to LTN config (don't exceed 2000 stacks) AND SET FILTERS in all loaders to match what each rocket is sending.
